{"tid":1917271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《武漢肺炎》WHO推特讚義大利做出偉大犧牲 慘遭網友轟爆！","createTime":"2020-03-09T11:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T12:15:05.000Z","uid":28114,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8edd349ea960a7d42b0ec53cf91192f9324046","tid":1917271,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/08/phpWu5DWj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F08%2FphpWu5DWj.jpg&h=be5f5766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎蔓延世界各地，義大利今日緊急下令，將全國4分之1人口強制隔離；對此，世界衛生組織秘書長譚德塞在推特稱讚，「義國做出真正的犧牲」，慘遭大批網友砲轟。資料照。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-09 00:04:22<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎蔓延世界各地，義大利今（8）日緊急下令，將全國4分之1人口強制隔離；對此，世界衛生組織秘書長譚德塞（Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus）在推特稱讚，「義國做出真正的犧牲」，慘遭大批網友砲轟。<br />\n<br />\n義大利今日累計逾5800起確診病例、223人死亡，總理孔蒂（Giuseppe Conte）已簽署法案，封鎖米蘭的倫巴底大區與境內14省份，將1600萬人口強制隔離，此人數約為義大利全國4分之1的人口。<br />\n<br />\n針對義大利疫情失控，不得已封城防疫措施，世衛組織秘書長譚德塞於推特發文表示，義大利人民正採取大膽、勇敢的步伐，減緩新型冠狀病毒蔓延，以保護國家和世界，他們做出真正的犧牲，WHO會與義大利站在一起，並持續支持各位。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞的推文引起各國網友不滿，紛紛在下方留言怒批，「到底什麼時候要宣布大流行？」、「如果中國政府不同意就不會宣布」、「你和WHO一、二月什麼事都沒做！現在誰來為確診者和死者負責？那些本不會接觸病毒的人，因爲開放邊境和旅遊被感染了，WHO要負責嗎？」、「與其寫這種沒有意義的幹話，不如告訴全世界都要戴口罩，並要求各國政府生產，叫民眾戴上它！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/08/phpFKoS01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F08%2FphpFKoS01.jpg&h=45fbd1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n譚德塞的貼文遭網友怒批，「與其寫這種沒有意義的幹話，不如告訴全世界都要戴口罩，並要求各國政府生產，叫民眾戴上它！」（圖擷取自Twitter）"},{"pid":"e94c87b2271677a4afae6c7ecf244829eec9db40","tid":1917271,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/03/08/phpQbRFP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F03%2F08%2FphpQbRFP4.jpg&h=3fed5373&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n世衛組織秘書長譚德塞引起推特網友諷刺，「到底什麼時候要宣布大流行？」、「如果中國政府不同意就不會宣布」。（圖擷取自Twitter）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3093030?utm_medium=P\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3093030%3Futm_medium%3DP&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM7vH1KbbL%2ByyGPsbuV3zdoQ%3D&h=80af9399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3093030%3Futm_medium%3DP&h=1d713897\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3093030?utm_medium=P</a>"},{"pid":"161336312c34e993950bd1fb61165eb815e4ee31","tid":1917271,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:42:06.000Z","msg":"意大利人被英雄"},{"pid":"939cf91aa28cd4b4db203a05c3236e1bbda20ceb","tid":1917271,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T11:52:26.000Z","msg":"WHO以為全世界都受呢套肉麻骨痺嘅客套說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fb7d80989761ea8fbea87ad1debb2d87e0b229","tid":1917271,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}